OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Four-day week on full pay 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fis here to stay'           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When Joe Dance was offered the chance  
OL,6, to earn his full salary by working just
OL,7, four days a week, he was sceptical.    
OL,9,F"I thought, I'm so used to working five
OL,10,Fdays. How are we going to deliver the  
OL,11,Fsame service for clients if we're not  
OL,12,Fthere?" the consultancy worker said.   
OL,14,FBut during a six-month trial where     
OL,15,F3,000 people worked fewer hours for    
OL,16,F100% pay, the new dad found his        
OL,17,Fproductivity improved.                 
OL,19,FThe experiment ended today and the     
OL,20,Fresults will be shared next year.      
